title: Caleb (footballer)
text:
Caleb Santos Jordão Rocha Carvalho (born 9 November 1992), known simply as Caleb, is a Brazilian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="S.C.%20Olhanense">SC Olhanense</a>.
Club career.
He made his professional debut in the <a href="Campeonato%20Brasileiro%20S%C3%A9rie%20A">Campeonato Brasileiro Série A</a> for <a href="Am%C3%A9rica%20Futebol%20Clube%20%28MG%29">América Mineiro</a> on 23 July 2011 in a game against <a href="Figueirense%20FC">Figueirense</a>.
